   <body>
      <div>
         <p>Only one unit might be in operation because:<ul>
               <li platform="PxW WxW">
                  <p>One unit is in <xref href="Hot_Standby_CPT_0000358503.xml" scope="local" type="concept"/>.</p>
               </li>
               <li>
                  <p>One unit is isolated.</p>
               </li>
               <li>
                  <p>One unit is inoperable.</p>
               </li>
            </ul>
         </p>
         <p>As an example, the active unit is shown in <ph platform="PxW WxW">normal operation</ph>
            <ph platform="SDC">float charge</ph> mode.</p>
         <note>The status of the parts and energized paths will
depend on the status of in the inactive unit and on the operation
mode of the active unit. </note>
